messages.message: @shiqi there was a bug discovered while testing on master. This is the bug fix that needs to be cherry-picked for 22.01. https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/30869
Can we wait till dogfood gets deployed and then verify the fix works on dogfood to merge to 22.01?

@Arjun unfortunately your change didn't make it to the last dogfood deployment and we have to wait till the current one finish to verify it on dogfood. I need to run some errands so I just merged the cp to 22.01, it should be deployed to the 22.01 release sandbox in a few hours, and if you can do a quick verify from there that will be great
